[DAY 23] PROPAGATION TYPES:
  REQUIRED     = join existing TX or create new one (default, 99% of cases)
  REQUIRES_NEW = suspend outer TX, create independent TX (audit, payments)
  NESTED       = savepoint within outer TX (Day 24)
  SUPPORTS     = join TX if exists, run without TX if not (read-only queries)
  NOT_SUPPORTED = suspend TX if exists, always run without TX
  MANDATORY    = must join existing TX, throw if none
  NEVER        = must not have TX, throw if one exists

  REQUIRES_NEW TRAP: Only works via proxy injection.
  this.auditLog() in same class = REQUIRED regardless of annotation.

